remarks.remarkText: Bird activity on & in vicinity of airport.
Declared low visibility conds require atct communication prior to push back.
Ppr ga aircraft on the psgr terminal apron, call operations 512-530-7550.
Taxiway a closed to aircraft with wingspan more than 171 ft.
Ppr for non state of texas aircraft entering the state ramp abeam taxiway E. call state operations 512-936-8900 or freq. 131.375.
Durg the hours 0000-0600 arriving aircraft will be assigned runway 35l or runway 35r & departing aircraft will be assigned runway 17l or runway 17r to avoid noise sensitive areas.
Noise abatement: all dep follow atc instructions; climb asap to 4000 ft or above.
Ppr engine maintenance run ups call operations 512-530-7550.
